      "author_association" : "NONE",
      "body" : "I think that you misunderstand the issue. The issue is not to improve the UI, it is to make it consistant on all the platform.s The current UI on windows does not have colors, does not have frames. It is the most used wallet. The Unix one has colors and has frames. MAC version does not have color but not have frames.\r\n\r\nBasically my changes will make the wallet identical on all the platforms. That means looking like the Unix version on all the version.\r\n\r\nI think it is a very important update, look at what the look of the UI for windows. Did you run a windows wallet once? it is awful.",
